name: Help End Cancer! Black "Get Your Pink On" Shirt
description:
Most everybody has been affected by this terrible disease in one way or another. We at Speak EZ Printing are commited to helping find the cure. During the month of October, we are offering this "Get Your Pink On" shirt, supporting Breast Cancer Awareness month. We will donate $5.00 from every shirt sold to the American Cancer Society.
Available in sizes Adult Small- Adult XL in White, Ash Grey or Black (see additional listings for colors)
Please help us reach our goal to donate $2500.00 for October. Get one for yourself, or possibly one for your entire office. Help us eliminate this disease once and for all!

name: 5 Football Shirts- Your Local School!!
description:
Show your local school football pride! Available with your school name, shirt color and one color lettering (specify when ordering). Tshirts on Gildan 100% preshrunk 5.3oz cotton. Available sizes Adult Small- Adult XL. Please specify sizes when ordering.
Larger sizes and quantities available. Contact me for pricing.

name: 20 Custom Printed T-Shirts, Your Design
description:
Promote your organization, hold a fund raiser, show your pride for an event, ANYTHING you desire. This listing is for 20 quality Gildan 100% Cotton or Gildan 50/50 Cotton/DryBlend Poly t-shirts on any color shirt with one color ink on front or back.

Available sizes are adult small to extra large. Larger sizes are available for an extra charge depending on the shirt color.

No setup charge is required. Supply your own artwork, or I can help create.

Most orders shipped within 3 business days of artwork approval.

CONTACT ME BEFORE PURCHASING as every customer has specific needs. I will create a special listing for you. 

Also contact  me for smaller and larger quantities. We are at your service and will do whatever we can to provide unbelievable service.
